==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Colporteur
<hw>Col"por`teur</hw> <pr>(?; 277)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[F.
<ets>colporteur</ets> one who carries on his neck, fr.
<ets>colporter</ets> to carry on one's neck; <ets>col</ets> (L.
<ets>collum</ets>) neck + <ets>porter</ets> (L. <ets>portare</ets>) to
carry.]</ety> <def>A hawker; specifically, one who travels about selling
and distributing religious tracts and books.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Colstaff</ent>⟦br⟧
